reviewText: Was not what I was looking for. Will give it to my pastor.
WE LOVED THE VIDEO. VERY OUSTANDING
Awesome extras to promote and reinforce the study.

Pages 11-19 are missing in my leader's guide. So far I have been unable to locate an address, phone number, etc.
to communicate with City on a Hill/ I will have to wing it it appears for these pages unless I can get a replacement.

This is a great set. It came timely and I had to make a return and the company was EXCELLENT to work with. However, you will need to buy the feature DVD separate as this only has the promotional products and the pastor's sermon info.
